snippet.title: Hero King Quest Peacemaker Prologue Opening
snippet.description:
Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1796080
Twitter: https://twitter.com/i_khaos
Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/SoundingStoneIndieGame

Hero King Quest: Peacemaker Prologue is a short "classic" JRPG. Play the role of the Dark Lord's sister, slay the Hero King, and take the first step in conquering humankind.
